###register user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Subhash",
    "email": "subhash@gmail.com",
    "password": "12345678"
}

###login user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "subhash@gmail.com",
    "password": "12345678"
}

###get authenticated user
GET http://localhost:5000/api/common/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YjhlNjUxZjY2NGFhZTczMGE4NjJkYyIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzcyNjYwOCwiZXhwIjoxNzc0MzMxNDA4fQ.VybyIVg2lnOio3zEoPHSUXwCDX33dT8NZ_9Wy5hdupI

###logout user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/logout
Content-Type: application/json

